(41, 1636, 'Richard Rosichan', 'Corona70@aol.com', '', '99.157.198.34', '2010-06-30 01:26:48', '2010-06-30 05:26:48', 'My wife and I are going to El Calafate for the eclipse. We have our hotel and a rental car. We\'re interested in joining with others to find a spot where we can have a clear view of the western horizon down to zero degrees above, or close to it, preferably near a road or roads to allow for last-minute mobility if needed. Please contact: Richard Rosichan, 2060 Alton Road, Miami Beach, Florida 33140-4563. Phone 305-674-9148. E mail: Corona70@aol.com. Thank you.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 8.0; Windows NT 5.1; Trident/4.0; GTB6.5; .NET CLR 1.0.3705; .NET CLR 1.1.4322; Media Center PC 4.0)', '', 0, 0),
