(7897, 3054, 'eg_video_description_long', 'The "Diamond Ring" phase of a Total Eclipse signals the beginning of totality, and the end of totality. You get two Diamond Rings every eclipse! Watch both in this clip from the Total Eclipse in Zambia, Africa in 2001.'),
