(7908, 3055, 'eg_video_description_short', 'Killer animation of the Moon\'s shadow sweeping through the sky!'),
(7909, 3055, '_eg_video_description_long', 'field_554439565a880'),
(7910, 3055, 'eg_video_description_long', 'In this clip from the Total Eclipse of December 2002 in the Outback, I have modified the speed and contrast in order to accentuate the movement of the Moon\'s shadow across the Earth. You don\'t get to see the Moon\'s umbra move like this everyday! Thanks to Klipsi for sharing his killer video.'),
