(7923, 3056, 'eg_video_description_long', 'In the Australian Outback in 2002, the Total Eclipse happened just before sunset. When the Sun hit the western horizon, the Moon was still in the way! This was a once-in-a-lifetime experience. Thanks to Klipsi for sharing his killer video.'),
