(8012, 3063, 'eg_video_description_short', 'Eclipseguy on CBC Radio Canada in 2006 talking about what he loves best.'),
(8013, 3063, '_eg_video_description_long', 'field_554439565a880'),
(8014, 3063, 'eg_video_description_long', 'A lot of media interest in my eclipse chasing was created when Toro Magazine published their account of my eclipse expedition to Libya in March 2006.  Cameron Phillips of CBC Radio in Vancouver called me up while I was at Burning Man that same year and invited me to speak on-air about my obsession.  Along with a few photos from the archive, here is the audio from the interview in its entirety.  Thanks to CBC.'),
