(8026, 3064, '_eg_video_description_long', 'field_554439565a880'),
(8027, 3064, 'eg_video_description_long', 'After multiple expeditions to the ice continent - including an eclipse trip in November 2003 - I have accumulated some amazing footage of icebergs and glaciers.  I couldn\'t resist putting together a short film dedicated to another of nature\'s most incredible creations - ice.'),
