(8040, 3065, 'eg_video_description_long', 'Part of my awesome eclipse chase to Libya in 2006 included bounding over orange sand dunes in 4x4s and camping in the desert with hardened local guides. Thought you might like to see what the Sahara Desert looks like - up close.'),
