(8052, 3066, '_eg_video_description_long', 'field_554439565a880'),
(8053, 3066, 'eg_video_description_long', 'Now In HD!! In 2006, eclipse chasers were treated to one of the most spectacular eclipses in recent history. In this film, The Sahara Desert in Libya provides the ultimate backdrop against which totality is observed. Best total eclipse sequence ever! I\'m not trying to make you jealous! Honest! If you only ever get to see a total eclipse on the internet you haven\'t lived yet!'),
