(8064, 3067, 'eg_video_description_short', 'Penguins! If you aren\'t convinced yet that eclipse chasing can take you EVERYWHERE - then check this one out.'),
(8065, 3067, '_eg_video_description_long', 'field_554439565a880'),
(8066, 3067, 'eg_video_description_long', 'In November 2003, I spent one month on a Russian icebreaker. Our team was the first in history to witness a Total Eclipse from the ice continent! This short film only begins to tell the story of how incredible this adventure was. And as you can see, we almost got clouded out for the eclipse!'),
