(8077, 3068, 'eg_video_description_short', 'Eclipses make it into the media all the time - with mixed results.  Check out the eclipse in this episode of ER.'),
(8078, 3068, '_eg_video_description_long', 'field_554439565a880'),
(8079, 3068, 'eg_video_description_long', 'As described in the Eclipse Film Database on this website, an episode of ER entitled "When Night Meets Day" employs a total solar eclipse. I\'ve put together the relevant scenes in this short clip so you can see how the eclipse was handled. Thanks to Warner Bros./NBC'),
