(8142, 3073, 'eg_video_description_short', 'On the way to the eclipse in Antarctica we saw some pretty amazing things.  Penguins!'),
(8143, 3073, '_eg_video_description_long', 'field_554439565a880'),
(8144, 3073, 'eg_video_description_long', 'Penguins are the coolest little animals.  Actually, the Emperors - made famous in film The March of the Penguins - are not that small!  Our expedition came across hundreds of Emperors by accident when we stopped the ship to hike to the "blue diamond" ice berg.  The shots of Adelie and Gentoo penguins are from other expeditions to the Antarctic Peninsula.'),
