(8195, 3077, '_eg_video_description_long', 'field_554439565a880'),
(8196, 3077, 'eg_video_description_long', 'The eclipse that almost wasn\'t! Freezing cold conditions - ice - snow - high winds - and a forecast of 90% overcast skies. A thrilling chase. And my first truly golden corona. Check it out!  Full trip report &amp; pix <a href="http://eclipseguy.com/tripreport/south-america-–-11-july-2010">here.</a>'),
