(8207, 3078, 'eg_video_description_short', 'Great Documentary Film.\r\nThe expedition to chase the Annular eclipse in Arizona in May 2012 went spectacularly well!  A must see!!'),
(8208, 3078, '_eg_video_description_long', 'field_554439565a880'),
(8209, 3078, 'eg_video_description_long', 'The mystique of the desert of the American southwest hung in the air with the eclipsed sun as we chased the Annular Eclipse of May 20, 2012, south of the Grand Canyon in Arizona.  Best eclipse video ever!  Turn up the speakers and go Full Screen!\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #71767a; font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: #f4f5f7; display: inline ! important; float: none;">\r\n</span>'),
