(8890, 3094, 'trip_report_sections_2_trip_report_section_content', '<figure><img src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/raventer.jpg" alt="aus rave enter" />  What\'s a festival without tons of banners and flags? (Notice they are all tilted to the right in the wind)</figure> <figure><img src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/ravestage.jpg" alt="aus rave stage" />  Dancin\' in a dust-bowl.</figure> <figure><img src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/selfportrait.jpg" alt="aus self port" />  (self-portrait) I\'m pretty sure that I consumed about a cup of sand that day.</figure> <figure><img src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/inthedust.jpg" alt="aus road dust" />  Less than an hour before the eclipse, hundreds of chasers line the road into Lyndhurst as a Festival transport truck kicks up the dust!</figure> '),
