(1302, 5, '2009-05-22 22:48:18', '2009-05-23 02:48:18', 'My friend Jim Huddle shot this amazing footage of the Total Eclipse in Antarctica in November 2003. From his location, the eclipse happened right on the horizon making this eclipse unique in the experience of eclipse chasers. I was in Antarctica as well for this one, but at a different location. Together, we were among the first humans to witness a Total Eclipse from Antarctica.', 'Antarctica Total Eclipse 2003', 0, 'It looks fake but this is real!!!!  Totality in Antarctica.  ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '618-revision-4', '', '', '2009-05-22 22:48:18', '2009-05-23 02:48:18', '', 618, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/618-revision-4', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
