bout how to handle life.Â  Life is so fleeting as well.', 'The eclipse as metaphor', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1354-revision-3', '', '', '2009-06-07 22:46:25', '2009-06-08 02:46:25', '', 1354, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/1354-revision-3', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
