(1379, 5, '2009-06-06 23:21:59', '2009-06-07 03:21:59', 'From the capital of Tripoli on the Mediterranean coast to the Great Sand Sea of the Sahara - Libya was unforgettable.  ', 'Shots from Libya', 0, 'The eclipse chase to Libya was one of the all-time best expeditions.  In many ways, the Sahara is the Earth at its most dramatic.  ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '467-revision-8', '', '', '2009-06-06 23:21:59', '2009-06-07 03:21:59', '', 467, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/467-revision-8', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1380, 5, '2009-06-06 23:56:18', '2009-06-07 03:56:18', 'I have been on four adventures to the poles with Quark Expeditions - once to the High Arctic and three times to Antarctica.  In December 2008 I was directing one of a series of promotional films for the company and took these shots for myself.  No eclipse on this one - but still worth seeing! \r\n\r\n', 'Antarctic Peninsula 2008', 0, 'Some stunning images from one of the most breath-taking regions of Earth.  ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '455-revision-12', '', '', '2009-06-06 23:56:18', '2009-06-07 03:56:18', '', 455, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/455-revision-12', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1382, 5, '2009-06-07 01:04:29', '2009-06-07 05:04:29', 'My friend Jim Huddle shot this amazing footage of the Total Eclipse in Antarctica in November 2003. From his location, the eclipse happened right on the horizon making this eclipse unique in the experience of eclipse chasers. I was in Antarctica as well for this one, but at a different location. Together, we were among the first humans to witness a Total Eclipse from Antarctica.', 'Antarctica Total Eclipse 2003', 0, 'It looks fake but this is real!!!!  Totality in Antarctica.  ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '618-revision-5', '', '', '2009-06-07 01:04:29', '2009-06-07 05:04:29', '', 618, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/618-revision-5', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1383, 5, '2009-06-07 15:03:37', '2009-06-07 19:03:37', 'The shadow of the Moon visits Earth next on 22 July 2009.\r\n\r\nWhere will you be?Â  Sitting at home?Â  At work?Â  Wasting time watching TV?\r\n\r\nForget all that.Â  Book a flight to Shanghai right now.Â  Come and see your first Total Solar Eclipse.\r\n<figure><img src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/TSE2009globe_400.jpg" alt="TSE2009_globe" />\r\nThe dark blue line is where you can see a Total Eclipse. Best place to see it is China.</figure>\r\n<figure><img src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/TSE2009_china_path.jpg" alt="TSE2009_path" />\r\n\r\nThis is the eclipse path through China.  Pick a city!  Let\'s go!\r\n\r\nImages Espenak/NASA/GSFC</figure>\r\n\r\nQuit wasting so much time.  Contact me immediately to get on an expedition - last minute!\r\n\r\n<a href="mailto:imoon@eclipseguy.staging.tunaheart.com">imoon@eclipseguy.staging.tunaheart.com</a>\r\n\r\nOr, post a comment right here! \r\n\r\nRemember:  Quit wasting your time not seeing a Total Solar Eclipse.  ', 'Total Solar Eclipse Only Days Away!', 0, 'Attention all readers!  Here is the PERFECT chance to see your first TSE!  This is the longest TSE of this century!  You will never get this chance again!\r\nQuit wasting so much time... ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1096-revision-24', '', '', '2009-06-07 15:03:37', '2009-06-07 19:03:37', '', 1096, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/1096-revision-24', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1384, 5, '2009-06-08 06:56:12', '2009-06-08 10:56:12', '<p style="text-align: left;">I am Canada\'s busiest eclipse chaser and this site is dedicated to the most spectacular natural event on Earth:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">A Total Solar Eclipse.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Most people will never witness a Total Eclipse in their lifetime - don\'t be one of them!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">I have witnessed 15 eclipses in 12 countries on 7 continents and I am continuously planning exotic adventures to strange and wonderful place on the Earth to stand in the shadow of the Moon!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Don\'t miss out on your chance! Act now to see a Total Solar Eclipse before you die!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>\r\n\r\n', 'You must see a Total Solar Eclipse at least once before you die!', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '352-revision-v1', '', '', '2009-06-08 06:56:12', '2009-06-08 10:56:12', '', 352, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/352-revision-34', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
