(2285, 5, '2014-11-14 15:47:05', '2014-11-14 19:47:05', '&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" alt="pitchman biz card" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/pitchman_card_1.jpg" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Since delivering my presentation at the Toronto TEDx Convention, I have been asked to speak at all kinds of meetings and on expeditions about our place in the universe - talking about what I have learned from two decades of eclipse chasing.  From this, my alter ego as "The Pitchman For The Universe" has taken shape.  Don\'t get me started!  In 2015, I am looking for opportunities to present my hour-long talk "Partnering With The Universe."</p>\n<img class="aligncenter" alt="dave talks at TED" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/ted_talk_1.jpg" />\n\nNuggets from the talk can be found under the "Musings" main navigation tab at the top of the page on this website.  You can view my TEDx video <a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/video/my-presentation-at-tedx-toronto" target="_self">here</a> - view a primer video for my talk <a href="http://vimeo.com/22826936" target="_blank">here</a> - and download the flyer in pdf format <a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/partnering_flyer2.pdf">here</a>.\n\nTo inquire about booking The Pitchman For The Universe, leave a comment at the bottom of this page, or contact me <a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/contact" target="_self">here</a>.\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" alt="dave talks at TED again" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/ted_talk_2.jpg" /></p>\n\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Partnering With The Universe</h2>\n<p style="text-align: left;">For 20 years, David Makepeace has travelled the world to witness Total Solar Eclipses - a natural phenomenon that has been called the most spectacular event you can witness from Earth.</p>\n"When the shadow of the Moon sweeps over us, we are brought into direct contact with a tangible presence that is awe-inspiring.  That there is a powerful relationship between us and the immense forces of the universe becomes undeniable."\n\nWhat possible relationship could you have to the universe?  How could it make a difference in your life?\n\nWith breathtaking film and video captured around the world at eclipse events, Makepeace takes us on a tour of our world and our solar system - widening the perspective on our lives as only an eclipse chaser can.  Discover how the simple beauty and mystery of our world can open the door to a greater awareness of what we are and our place in the universe.', 'Speaking Engagements', 0, 'The Pitchman For The Universe is on tour in 2014.  Come see my inspiring presentation about our place in the universe.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2261-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-11-14 15:47:05', '2014-11-14 19:47:05', '', 2261, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2261-autosave', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
