awesome interactive, Google maps for this eclipse from Xavier Jubier.', 'The Next Eclipse ', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2296-revision-v1', '', '', '2011-07-20 15:16:00', '2011-07-20 19:16:00', '', 2296, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2296-revision-10', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
