(2341, 5, '2011-07-20 16:01:46', '2011-07-20 20:01:46', '<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/pitchman_card_1.jpg" alt="pitchman biz card" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Since delivering my presentation at the Toronto TEDx Convention, I have been asked to speak at all kinds of meetings and on expeditions about our place in the universe - and what I have learned from two decades of eclipse chasing.  From this, my alter ego as "The Pitchman For The Universe" has taken shape.  Don\'t get me started!</p>\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/ted_talk_1.jpg" alt="dave talks at TED" />\r\n\r\nOn August 15, 2011, I will be at Wavelengths Yoga in Norwood, Ontario, Canada, to deliver "Partnering With The Universe."  Excerpts from the talk can be found under the "Musings" main navigation tab at the top of the page on this website - and see my TED video <a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/video/my-presentation-at-tedx-toronto" target="_self">here</a>.\r\n\r\nStay tuned for more dates coming soon!  And to inquire about booking The Pitchman For The Universe, leave a comment at the bottom of this page, or contact me <a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/contact" target="_self">here</a>.\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/ted_talk_2.jpg" alt="dave talks at TED again" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/makepeace_partnering_1.jpg" alt="wavelengths ad" /></p>', 'Speaking Engagements', 0, 'The Pitchman For The Universe is on tour in 2011.  Come see my inspiring presentation about our place in the universe.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2261-revision-v1', '', '', '2011-07-20 16:01:46', '2011-07-20 20:01:46', '', 2261, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2261-revision-33', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
