(2387, 5, '2012-05-23 14:00:45', '2012-05-23 18:00:45', '<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/video/beads-in-arizona"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/annularity_thumb.jpg" alt="news annularity 2012" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<figure>While thousands of onlookers enjoyed the May 20 annular eclipse from places like the Grand Canyon and Zion National Park, a small team of us ventured to the eclipse path\'s southern limit in Arizona to try to catch a glimpse of the "edge phenomenon" that is only visible during this kind of eclipse.  And what a great idea it was!  <a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/video/beads-in-arizona">See the brand new documentary here</a>.</figure>', 'Success In The Desert!', 0, 'Spectacular annular eclipse bedazzles thousands in the American southwest May 20.  \r\nBrand New Documentary Film', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'success-in-the-desert', '', 'http://eclipseguy.dev/video/beads-in-arizona\nhttp://eclipseguy.dev/video/beads-in-arizona', '2012-06-30 23:29:04', '2012-07-01 03:29:04', '', 0, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/?p=2387', 0, 'post', '', 0),
