(2453, 5, '2012-05-23 14:02:23', '2012-05-23 18:02:23', '<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/annularity_thumb.jpg" alt="news annularity 2012" /></p>\r\n\r\n<figure>While thousands of onlookers enjoyed the May 20 annular eclipse from places like the Grand Canyon and Zion National Park, a small team of us ventured to the eclipse path\'s southern limit in Arizona to try to catch a glimpse of the "edge phenomenon" that is only visible during this kind of eclipse.  And what a great idea it was!  I have just returned home - working on the video right now.  Come back in a few days!</figure>', 'Success In The Desert!', 0, 'Spectacular annular eclipse bedazzles thousands in the American southwest May 20.  ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2387-revision-4', '', '', '2012-05-23 14:02:23', '2012-05-23 18:02:23', '', 2387, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2387-revision-4', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2454, 5, '2012-06-11 22:45:19', '2012-06-12 02:45:19', '<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/annularity_thumb.jpg" alt="news annularity 2012" /></p>\r\n\r\n<figure>While thousands of onlookers enjoyed the May 20 annular eclipse from places like the Grand Canyon and Zion National Park, a small team of us ventured to the eclipse path\'s southern limit in Arizona to try to catch a glimpse of the "edge phenomenon" that is only visible during this kind of eclipse.  And what a great idea it was!  See the brand new documentary here.</figure>', 'Success In The Desert!', 0, 'Spectacular annular eclipse bedazzles thousands in the American southwest May 20.  ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2387-revision-5', '', '', '2012-06-11 22:45:19', '2012-06-12 02:45:19', '', 2387, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/2387-revision-5', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
