(2580, 5, '2012-06-05 23:37:51', '2012-06-06 03:37:51', 'During the eclipse expedition to China in 2008, we passed through the city of Xi\'an and had the chance to see the famous Terracotta Warriors. More than 8,000 warriors, horses and chariots have been uncovered.  They were created in 246 BC but not discovered until 1974. My invitation into the private area in the facility to film the warriors that are being repaired allowed me to get amazing, close up pictures of these sculptures.', 'The Terracotta Warriors', 0, 'The magnificent Terracotta Warriors!  Unique, behind-the-scenes footage - rarely seen like this. ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '958-revision-8', '', '', '2012-06-05 23:37:51', '2012-06-06 03:37:51', '', 958, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/958-revision-8', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
