(2733, 5, '2012-06-05 23:36:14', '2012-06-06 03:36:14', 'After the TSE in Zambia in June, 2001, I went on Safari in Malawi.  This clip is from the half-hour film I produced about the expedition.', 'Malawi Safari', 0, 'A life-long dream to go on safari in Africa comes true in 2001.  Eclipses rule.  ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '971-revision-4', '', '', '2012-06-05 23:36:14', '2012-06-06 03:36:14', '', 971, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/971-revision-4', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2734, 5, '2012-06-05 23:37:02', '2012-06-06 03:37:02', 'While most cameras are pointed at the sky during a Total Eclipse, the best way to get a sense of what it feels like to be there is to witness what is happening to the people on the ground. In this clip, watch as the Moon\'s shadow arrives, then retreats, from our observing spot - an ancient archeological site 1,000 feet above the Tigris River in Southern Turkey. So killer!', 'Darkness in Turkey 1999', 0, 'One of the best ways to get a sense of a Total Eclipse is not to watch the sky... but watch the people on the ground! Daytime turns into night before your eyes!', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '967-revision-4', '', '', '2012-06-05 23:37:02', '2012-06-06 03:37:02', '', 967, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/967-revision-4', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
