(2937, 5, '2014-11-14 19:47:26', '2014-11-14 23:47:26', '<h1>You must see a\r\nTotal Solar Eclipse\r\nat least once before you die!</h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">I am Canada\'s busiest eclipse chaser and this site is dedicated to the most spectacular natural event on Earth:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>A Total Solar Eclipse.</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Most people will never witness a Total Eclipse in their lifetime - don\'t be one of them!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">I have witnessed 20 eclipses in 13 countries on 7 continents and I am continuously planning exotic adventures to strange and wonderful places on the Earth to stand in the shadow of the Moon!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Don\'t miss out on your chance! Act now to see a Total Solar Eclipse before you die!</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1447" title="canada" alt="canada" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/canada.gif" width="68" height="50" /></p>', 'Home', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '352-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-14 19:47:26', '2014-11-14 23:47:26', '', 352, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/uncategorized/352-revision-60', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
