(3194, 5, '2015-04-22 18:56:09', '2015-04-22 22:56:09', '<a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/?p=2966">Read the Trip Report here</a>.\r\n\r\nHere is the first look at our successful observation of the Total Solar Eclipse of March 20, 2015 from our Air Berlin 737 high above the North Sea.  We are all very happy!  This was an incredibly exciting chase and my first from the air.  My 21st eclipse!  Short film in the works!\r\n<a href="http://nordlandseite.de/berichte/reise/sonnenfinsternis2015.htm" target="_blank">\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/TSE_2015_GROUP_PHOTO_600.jpeg"><img class="size-full wp-image-2953 aligncenter" alt="TSE_2015_GROUP_PHOTO_600" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/TSE_2015_GROUP_PHOTO_600.jpeg" width="600" height="235" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<figure><a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web-600.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-2922 aligncenter" alt="tse 2015 web 600" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web-600.png" width="600" height="375" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The beginning of totality and the Diamond Ring.</p>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure><a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web3-600.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-2932 aligncenter" alt="tse-2015-web3-600" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web3-600.jpg" width="600" height="375" /></a>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The stunning sight of the Moon\'s shadow sweeping down from space and crossing the Earth.\r\nIce crystals on the window!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2933" alt="tse-2015-web2-600" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/tse-2015-web2-600.jpg" width="600" height="375" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Mid-totality.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/Malicki_totality_2015.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-2955 aligncenter" alt="Malicki_totality_2015" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/Malicki_totality_2015.jpg" width="630" height="419" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<figure>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Gorgeous wide shot of mid-totality from Chris Malicki. Surreal view!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">And watch the Moon\'s shadow race across the North Sea in this satellite animation ...</p>\r\n<iframe src="https://vine.co/v/OYAhHMbvjYp/embed/postcard" height="600" width="600" frameborder="0"></iframe><script type="text/javascript" src="https://platform.vine.co/static/scripts/embed.js"></script></figure>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"></p>', 'Success at 37,000 ft. above the North Sea!', 0, 'Only weeks ago, eclipse flight out of Germany stuns chasers with never-before-seen views.  ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2921-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-22 18:56:09', '2015-04-22 22:56:09', '', 2921, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/2921-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
