rget="_blank">website</a>.', 'Total Eclipse in 2012', 0, 'There is a Total Eclipse in 2012! \r\nCan you guess where? ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2349-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-11 13:13:45', '2015-06-11 17:13:45', '', 2349, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/2349-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
