(3272, 4, '2015-07-06 05:28:31', '2015-07-06 09:28:31', '<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/st_cover1_600.jpg" alt="s&amp;t_news_cover" /></p>\r\n\r\n<figure>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Any fan of the sky wants to appear in the pages of Sky &amp; Telescope!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The article in the July 2012 issue of Sky &amp; Telescope features extreme eclipse chasers and the lengths to which they will go to stand in the shadow of the Moon.  Dean Regas interviewed me about my extreme chase to South America in 2010 - an expedition that could have gone all wrong.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/QuestForTotality.pdf">Download the entire article here</a>.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.skyandtelescope.com/skytel/beyondthepage/The-Quest-for-Totality-147992355.html" target="_blank">Here is the link to the S&amp;T website - where they feature a few of my eclipse chasing videos, too</a>.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\r\n\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://eclipseguy.dev/wp-content/uploads/st_detail_600.jpg" alt="s&amp;t inside page" /></p>\r\n\r\n<figure>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">I am almost famous now for sure!</p>\r\n\r\n</figure>', 'Cool Article About Me in Sky & Telescope Magazine', 0, 'Extreme Eclipse Chasers in the Quest For Totality is the subject of this July 2012 article by Dean Regas from the Cincinnati Observatory.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2510-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-06 05:28:31', '2015-07-06 09:28:31', '', 2510, 'http://eclipseguy.dev/2510-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
